WEBVTT

01:11.208 --> 01:17.000
Through incessant rains
and scorching sun

01:17.583 --> 01:22.167
With the wind blowing strong

01:23.417 --> 01:29.542
Rising enmity make heads fall

01:29.708 --> 01:34.292
Life sometimes does cease

01:35.708 --> 01:46.625
Through day and night,
you protect us.

01:47.750 --> 01:58.667
You come in godly
forms, to guard us.

01:59.708 --> 02:04.500
Trees may collapse

02:06.125 --> 02:10.292
Seeds nurture life within

02:11.917 --> 02:21.000
Fall to rise and fight.

02:54.750 --> 02:57.583
Through mornings
that never starts

02:58.333 --> 03:01.000
Through days that never end

03:01.375 --> 03:07.042
You toil ever persistent

03:07.583 --> 03:12.875
There exists no state
Free of crimes till date

03:13.042 --> 03:17.375
Hunt them with a just view

03:19.667 --> 03:24.625
In your sleep...

03:31.208 --> 03:37.250
Vigilant even in your sleep

03:37.833 --> 03:43.208
Your methods stay
when you are gone

03:43.833 --> 03:48.750
Enormous works are done

03:49.833 --> 03:54.792
No one can replace the force

04:36.708 --> 04:38.250
Hey listen

04:38.500 --> 04:39.333
Shut up

04:39.667 --> 04:40.167
Don't irritate

04:40.333 --> 04:44.542
Had I married someone else
I would've been happier

04:44.792 --> 04:46.042
You keep quiet!

04:46.333 --> 04:46.875
Don’t raise your voice

04:47.042 --> 04:48.833
- I know what to do
- What do you know?

04:49.250 --> 04:50.542
- Don’t you...
- How dare...

04:50.667 --> 04:54.042
Mind your own business. Don’t you
poke your nose into my business.

04:54.208 --> 04:58.667
- How dare you...
- Don't you dare lay your hands on me.

05:03.500 --> 05:04.708
How dare you hit a woman?

05:05.042 --> 05:06.042
She is my wife

05:06.250 --> 05:07.625
Will you hit her in a public
place if she is wife?

05:07.792 --> 05:08.958
Hey. Tell him!

05:09.208 --> 05:10.292
He is my husband.

05:10.500 --> 05:11.833
Keep all your arguments at home.

05:12.208 --> 05:13.292
I'll have you arrested.

05:13.375 --> 05:15.667
