Why didn't you pick your mobile?

26:20.292 --> 26:21.125
I don't know where I placed it.

26:21.792 --> 26:22.458
I didn’t hear it ring.

26:23.625 --> 26:25.542
Call your parents and
wish them after you eat.

26:26.042 --> 26:26.875
Why?

26:27.292 --> 26:28.500
Today is their
wedding anniversary.

26:29.500 --> 26:31.833
- Oh my! I forgot. Bye bye.
- Ok.

26:32.125 --> 26:34.417
- Hey! Hello hello
- Yes.

26:35.708 --> 26:38.708
- You too please wish them.
- I'll think about it.

26:39.458 --> 26:42.042
If not for my dad,
at least wish my mom.

26:42.375 --> 26:45.125
I am here for a case.
I'll finish this first.

26:46.292 --> 26:47.583
Thanks for coming.
Please take your seat.

26:48.208 --> 26:49.792
Two teas here.

26:53.833 --> 26:56.458
This is regarding SI Subburaj's case.

26:57.042 --> 27:01.708
I have a few doubts in that murder. I
wanted to meet you to discuss that.

27:02.583 --> 27:04.208
I am clear about three things of that case.

27:04.500 --> 27:07.583
Firstly, he does not have any
official or personal enemies.

27:08.000 --> 27:11.042
Secondly, this is a well planned murder.

27:11.500 --> 27:13.875
Thirdly, Subburaj was off duty that day.

27:14.292 --> 27:16.125
It was Kanagavel who was
supposed to be there.

27:16.875 --> 27:18.958
What if Subburaj was killed
instead of Kanagavel?

27:22.250 --> 27:25.292
If you can provide me details about
Kanagavel, I can proceed further.

27:26.000 --> 27:30.292
Hold on. Who gave you the permission to
enter my station and browse the records?

27:30.792 --> 27:32.125
What right do you have?

27:32.500 --> 27:35.000
I tried many times to reach you.
But I couldn't.

27:35.333 --> 27:38.542
How did you reach me now?

27:39.125 --> 27:40.458
You could have tried
the same way.

27:42.042 --> 27:45.125
- Sorry sir. Please leave that.
- Hold on!

27:45.292 --> 27:51.417
This isn't a soccer match to
kill someone instead of another.

27:51.917 --> 27:53.375
First investigate properly.

27:54.750 --> 27:59.375
What you said, looks like anyone with a cop's
attire would be been killed that night.

28:00.000 --> 28:01.375
Make a move!

28:02.583 --> 28:03.875
He is the sub inspector
of your station.

28:04.292 --> 28:06.250
- If you don’t co-operate...
- I am telling you the same.

28:06.500 --> 28:08.250
Why are you more worried
about it than us?

28:08.708 --> 28:13.458
You accept bribes and investigate
as a honest officer.

28:15.125 --> 28:17.167
- Wasting my time.
- Thank you.

28:19.583 --> 28:20.083
Hello

28:22.167 --> 28:24.667
Shall I enter your house when you are away?

28:25.333 --> 28:26.583
It feels the same for us too.

28:27.083 --> 28:30.208
You don't have an
answer to my question.

28:30.542 --> 28:32.667
Why should I answer
your questions?

28:33.208 --> 28:34.792
As though he is a big shot!

28:37.208 --> 28:39.208
What?

28:46.208 --> 28:47.833
Calm down. Please sit down.

28:54.750 --> 28:55.250
Sir tea.

29:02.375 --> 29:05.458
You haven't got the order
of becoming the ACP yet.

29:05.625 --> 29:10.625
With all these incidents, I can
easily stop your promotion.

29:10.792 --> 29:15.292
- I can't work considering...
- What are you trying to say? How can you hit an Inspector?

29:15.667 --> 29:19.375
- He didn't co-operate with me.
- What results have you got?

29:19.875 --> 29:21.042
Should I speak up or not?

29:23.333 --> 29:23.833
Tell me.

29:24.708 --> 29:27.917
To save Kanagavel, Subburaj has given
his life without his knowledge.

29:30.375 --> 29:31.042
Please take a look.

29:39.583 --> 29:41.125
I don't have any personal
vengeance against him.

29:41.667 --> 29:43.583
I am very sure that he is
also involved in this case.

29:44.208 --> 29:45.875
You inquire me for
hitting an inspector.

29:46.292 --> 29:48.125
It is because of him that the
wife of a cop is now a widow.

29:49.042 --> 29:50.250
What is your answer to them?

29:50.875 --> 29:52.250
That, your husband is dead?

29:52.708 --> 29:53.875
That, you can save on
the funeral expenses?

29:55.708 --> 29:57.833
We need to show them what happens
if they lay their hands on cops.

29:59.875 --> 30:01.583
I will not spare anyone
involved in this case.

30:09.125 --> 30:10.833
I cannot work for promotions.

30:20.250 --> 30:21.750
Hey! What are you
still doing here?

30:22.000 --> 30:22.958
Didn't I ask you to leave?

30:23.667 --> 30:24.750
Should I arrange a
farewell party?

30:25.417 --> 30:27.417
He has started digging deeper.

30:27.583 --> 30:31.292
Leave the place or I will
kill you and you child.

30:32.958 --> 30:35.042
I am talking to you and...

31:08.625 --> 31:09.375
Sir! Sir!

31:13.292 --> 31:13.792
Sir

31:19.083 --> 31:19.917
Where are they?

31:34.833 --> 31:35.333
Sir!

31:36.375 --> 31:36.875
Are you fine?

31:37.500 --> 31:38.875
I am alright sir!

31:50.417 --> 31:51.167
Oh my!

31:53.542 --> 31:55.250
Sir.. Sir...

32:02.417 --> 32:03.292
What are you doing here?

32:03.375 --> 32:04.750
Sir. Please go.

32:04.875 --> 32:08.083
I am acting as though am buying groceries.
Its a plan to catch them.

32:09.208 --> 32:09.708
Please go.

32:10.292 --> 32:12.583
I am on the run. Can you please
inform me, if you get hold of them?

32:12.708 --> 32:14.000
Sure sir!

32:31.292 --> 32:32.417
Run! Cops!

34:26.583 --> 34:28.042
Please spare us.

34:28.292 --> 34:30.750
Please forgive us.
We'll not do it again.

34:34.458 --> 34:36.917
How dare you lay your hands
on a police officer?

34:37.042 --> 34:39.500
It was a mistake.
Please spare us.

34:40.250 --> 34:41.917
Sorry sir.

34:41.958 --> 34:43.750
You mercilessly
burnt him alive...

34:43.792 --> 34:45.042
Sorry sir.

34:45.167 --> 34:45.958
...and now you ask forgiveness!

35:05.750 --> 35:07.708
Sir. I'll tell you everything.

35:08.167 --> 35:09.875
I will tell you everything.

35:10.167 --> 35:12.542
I will tell you everything sir.

35:12.708 --> 35:13.917
I don't care to spare you.

35:14.667 --> 35:18.042
I will tell you everything.
Please save me.

35:18.208 --> 35:19.542
I will be killed if I
tell you anything.

35:19.750 --> 35:21.208
Do you want to die now or
after a couple of days?

35:21.542 --> 35:22.833
You want security?

35:23.333 --> 35:24.042
Tell me the truth.

35:28.708 --> 35:29.458
Its Vaathiyar.

35:30.042 --> 35:34.083
Markets, travels, granite, real
estate, timber and other businesses.

35:34.417 --> 35:36.458
He controls the entire
central market.

35:37.083 --> 35:38.917
Nothing happens without
his knowledge.

35:39.333 --> 35:40.167
Not just that.

35:40.625 --> 35:43.458
No one dares to enter the Police
station without his permission.

35:43.917 --> 35:47.875
He is the force and he is the law.

35:50.625 --> 35:52.458
Greetings sir!

35:53.083 --> 35:53.875
Greetings!

35:55.250 --> 35:56.125
Sit down.

35:59.542 --> 36:01.542
Chelladurai wishes
to be the leader.

36:01.875 --> 36:02.750
Let's fulfill his wish.

36:03.667 --> 36:06.458
Listen Chelladurai. Becoming
the leader is not a big task.

36:06.667 --> 36:09.167
But if hear anything
wrong about you..

36:09.500 --> 36:11.083
That will be the end of it.

36:11.208 --> 36:12.208
Yes sir. Your blessings please.

36:15.250 --> 36:16.500
Greetings.

36:21.458 --> 36:25.000
- I'll go to court.
- Oh! You are going to the court is it?

36:27.292 --> 36:30.750
Siblings issue. He is going
to the court it seems.

36:31.375 --> 36:32.583
Are you going to the court?

36:32.833 --> 36:34.250
No sir.

36:34.500 --> 36:35.792
Just listen and follow what he says.

36:36.167 --> 36:38.042
Do you understand?
Have something and leave.

36:50.292 --> 36:51.417
Vaathiyar has a single daughter.

36:52.417 --> 36:56.583
As per her wishes, Vaathiyar did
not bother about the status...

36:56.875 --> 36:58.667
...and got her married to
sub inspector Kanagavel.

36:59.667 --> 37:01.583
She did not like
her life with him

37:02.750 --> 37:06.542
Kanagavel was content with his earnings
and did not seek out to Vaathiyar.

37:07.542 --> 37:09.083
They quarreled everyday.

37:09.333 --> 37:11.292
I'll send people when I reach

37:11.458 --> 37:13.667
You better sign the divorce papers...

37:19.583 --> 37:20.542
Please call this off dad.

37:20.833 --> 37:26.833
Kanagavel did not sign the divorce papers
out of fear of losing his daughter.

37:27.458 --> 37:31.167
Vaathiyar mediated the issue
and Kanagavel did not respect him.

37:31.208 --> 37:32.000
What?

37:32.958 --> 37:35.667
Vaathiyar bore all
this for his daughter.

37:35.833 --> 37:38.458
This is how am
struggling everyday.

37:38.958 --> 37:40.875
Dad!!

37:41.875 --> 37:46.333
The quarrel kept aggravating and
one day Kanagavel hit his wife.

37:46.792 --> 37:49.792
She said that she would
no longer live with him.

37:50.375 --> 37:51.958
She wanted to be separated
from him permanently.

37:52.625 --> 37:56.542
She said that, to be peaceful she did
not even care if her husband was dead.

37:57.625 --> 37:59.125
Now that his daughter has said this...

37:59.750 --> 38:04.417
Vaathiyar decided to finish off Kanagavel
without bothering about the consequences.

38:06.625 --> 38:08.083
The day they planned to murder Kanagavel...

38:08.792 --> 38:09.917
...he met with an accident.

38:10.250 --> 38:12.125
So instead of him, Subburaj
was assigned for night duty.

38:12.542 --> 38:14.917
The contract killers mistook Subburaj
for Kanagavel...

38:15.417 --> 38:16.625
...and killed him.

38:17.167 --> 38:17.958
This is what happened.

38:19.042 --> 38:21.958
Let's take legal action.
Wait for the order.

38:22.250 --> 38:23.500
- Ok?
- Yes Sir

38:54.250 --> 38:55.833
Mom had called.

38:57.667 --> 38:58.833
Pooja holidays are nearing.

38:59.042 --> 39:01.375
Mom wanted to see the kids.

39:02.250 --> 39:03.375
The phone is ringing. Get it.

39:04.042 --> 39:04.833
Get me the phone.

39:11.167 --> 39:12.167
Switch it on and give it.

39:15.750 --> 39:17.458
- Hello.
- Is it Mr.Sethu?

39:18.333 --> 39:19.208
Greetings sir.

39:19.583 --> 39:22.042
- I am Mathivaanan from Vaathiyar's house.
- Tell me what the matter is.

39:22.750 --> 39:25.750
Nothing. Uncle wanted to talk to you.

39:26.208 --> 39:30.292
If you can give an appointment, Vaathiyar
would like to discuss with you in person.

39:31.000 --> 39:33.708
It is something big that he
is coming down to meet you.

39:35.583 --> 39:36.083
Hello

39:41.750 --> 39:42.250
He hung up.

39:43.917 --> 39:45.708
Mom had called.

39:46.042 --> 39:48.333
Tell me what the matter is. You've
been beating around the bush.

39:50.458 --> 39:52.750
She wanted to see all of
us and told us to visit.

39:53.083 --> 39:54.542
If you want you can go.
Why are you asking me?

39:55.375 --> 39:56.833
Did I talk so much to go alone?

39:57.083 --> 39:58.417
What do you want me to do?

39:58.667 --> 40:01.125
Dad is old. Why can't you
compromise with him?

40:01.750 --> 40:02.792
I am saying the same.

40:03.250 --> 40:04.458
Your father has grown old.

40:05.208 --> 40:06.250
Why can't he compromise?

40:17.958 --> 40:18.458
Hey!

40:20.375 --> 40:21.167
Serve chutney.

40:22.500 --> 40:23.208
Fatso!

40:30.625 --> 40:31.333
What?

40:32.167 --> 40:33.417
Will he fall in our line?

40:34.458 --> 40:36.500
Will he even have a choice?

40:36.875 --> 40:39.625
I'll meet him directly and seal the deal.
I'll meet you after that.

40:53.583 --> 40:55.167
Hey darling. How is it?

40:56.875 --> 40:57.375
Sir

40:57.833 --> 41:01.125
Mathivaanan from Vaathiyar's
house has come to meet you.

41:03.542 --> 41:04.875
Check if the fax machine
is switched on.

41:05.375 --> 41:07.458
Ok Sir. Mathivaanan...

41:11.000 --> 41:13.000
I told you to check
the fax machine.

41:15.250 --> 41:16.042
Hey darling.

41:16.417 --> 41:17.458
Sorry fatso!

41:17.583 --> 41:18.750
Here he is.

41:19.375 --> 41:20.167
Can we meet him?

41:20.792 --> 41:24.042
He is not in a good mood.
He is furious.

41:24.125 --> 41:25.708
It's getting late. I can't
explain things to uncle.

41:25.750 --> 41:26.542
Moses.

41:31.667 --> 41:33.833
- Sir.
- What were you discussing, Moses?

41:34.292 --> 41:37.542
Nothing sir. They
are known to me.

41:37.833 --> 41:40.625
If they are known to you, why are
you chit chatting with them here?

41:41.958 --> 41:43.750
Keep your all your
relationships at your house.

41:45.333 --> 41:46.167
This is my station.

41:46.958 --> 41:48.292
Go now.

41:54.042 --> 41:54.542
Hey!

41:55.958 --> 41:57.833
- Fill all the details here.
- Hey Moses.

41:59.875 --> 42:00.458
Listen

42:04.292 --> 42:06.042
Hey! Won't you be quiet?

42:07.292 --> 42:09.000
I am going to thrash you!

42:26.458 --> 42:28.000
- When did you lose it?
- Last week.

42:28.250 --> 42:29.333
- Murthy
- Sir

42:29.750 --> 42:31.542
- Is the fax ready?
- Yes sir. We can leave.

42:31.583 --> 42:32.542
Hello sir. We've been waiting....

42:32.583 --> 42:35.792
Fill the address clearly.
We'll look into it.

42:37.958 --> 42:40.625
We know it. Won't we
inform you if we get it.

42:41.083 --> 42:42.583
Inspector is leaving for a work.

42:43.708 --> 42:46.125
Sir. I've been
wanting to meet you.

42:46.542 --> 42:48.375
There is no information
about my chain.

42:48.625 --> 42:51.542
- Can you please help me?
- How long will you take?

42:52.125 --> 42:52.875
I am looking into it sir.

42:54.000 --> 42:55.042
Do I have to
constantly follow up?

42:56.542 --> 42:57.208
Idiot.

42:58.250 --> 42:59.583
You will get your
chain in two days.

43:00.208 --> 43:02.292
Please leave now.

43:03.083 --> 43:03.792
Trust us.

43:05.292 --> 43:06.042
Madam

43:06.333 --> 43:08.250
- Where did you say the incident happened?
- Near Ganesh theater

43:09.625 --> 43:10.292
Ok. Please leave.

43:13.208 --> 43:14.667
I am looking into it sir.

43:22.000 --> 43:24.042
There is nothing
impossible for me here.

43:24.458 --> 43:25.625
This is just a small issue.

43:26.250 --> 43:28.125
The murder should've been neat.

43:28.500 --> 43:29.458
A small mistake and...

43:29.875 --> 43:31.500
...today that guy is alive.

43:32.000 --> 43:33.292
We'll see for how long that is.

43:34.000 --> 43:36.375
Otherwise, I don't even know
the guy who was killed.

43:36.833 --> 43:39.542
What needs to be done for
his family will be done. Better than ever.

43:39.833 --> 43:41.750
What will the government do?

43:43.833 --> 43:44.542
Sir. It's ready.

43:45.667 --> 43:48.375
Is it? Just a moment.

44:31.875 --> 44:34.417
Why haven't you had
the coffee yet?

44:34.667 --> 44:35.583
No, thanks sir.

44:39.458 --> 44:40.417
What was I saying?

44:42.167 --> 44:44.458
I don't even know the
guy who was killed.

44:44.792 --> 44:46.292
To the family of that guy...

44:46.500 --> 44:47.875
...I will do what is required.
That's my responsibility.

44:48.417 --> 44:51.083
- Dad!
- Yes dear.

44:51.208 --> 44:53.750
- Send my kid. She will start crying out of hunger.
- Go and eat dear.

44:54.458 --> 44:58.458
Dear, he is the inspector
I told you about.

44:58.542 --> 44:59.708
Greetings.

45:01.625 --> 45:05.667
My glance is enough for my
guys to fulfill my orders.

45:06.500 --> 45:09.167
But, shouldn't we respect you for having
respected our call and making it here.

45:10.417 --> 45:11.917
Please walk out from this case.

45:12.417 --> 45:14.042
I'll offer whatever
is required for that.

45:14.792 --> 45:17.625
Either ways is fine for me.
What do you say?

45:19.292 --> 45:20.667
Now you have to decide.

45:27.917 --> 45:28.417
Sir!

45:29.167 --> 45:31.500
Speak out one more word and you'll
hear all the foul language I know!

45:33.083 --> 45:35.833
Keep calm and board the vehicle.
Or else, I'll thrash and take you!

45:35.875 --> 45:37.667
What are you saying?

45:39.292 --> 45:41.500
How dare you?

45:48.708 --> 45:49.208
Murthy

45:55.708 --> 45:58.125
Who is this Police officer?

45:58.250 --> 46:00.458
He has dared to lay hands
on Vaathiyar himself.

46:00.875 --> 46:05.583
No one can even question him.

46:06.042 --> 46:12.042
He has been our strength.
Now he is being arrested.

46:14.667 --> 46:16.542
This cop shows a lot of attitude.

46:33.208 --> 46:33.708
Sir!

46:34.083 --> 46:34.583
Sir!

46:34.958 --> 46:37.167
Wait! Where are you going?

46:37.208 --> 46:38.542
- How long should we wait?
- He has just come.

46:38.708 --> 46:42.083
- Please inform him. How long should we wait?
- Please keep quiet.

46:43.625 --> 46:46.292
Please be seated.

46:55.958 --> 46:58.208
Uncle!

46:59.417 --> 47:00.833
Why are you here?

47:01.667 --> 47:02.417
Speak out uncle.

47:02.917 --> 47:04.792
Hey! Hey you!

47:05.333 --> 47:07.042
Sir is calling you. Come inside.

47:07.208 --> 47:09.292
I'll talk to him.

47:17.708 --> 47:19.083
- Sir
- Yes

47:19.250 --> 47:19.833
They are here.

47:21.625 --> 47:22.125
Tell me.

47:22.750 --> 47:25.333
I understand that you've been
waiting from morning. Tell me.

47:30.542 --> 47:31.750
Why are you guys blinking?

47:32.500 --> 47:33.708
Tell me what the matter is.

47:36.833 --> 47:40.417
Murthy. They are staring at me and
its funny! Ask them to leave!

47:43.167 --> 47:44.542
Hey! Leave now.

47:45.125 --> 47:47.667
- Don't make me laugh.
- Go now.

47:52.708 --> 47:53.208
Uncle

47:57.333 --> 47:57.833
Uncle

47:58.750 --> 48:00.292
I can't stand this sight!

48:04.708 --> 48:05.875
I'll be back with
the lawyer soon.

48:06.250 --> 48:08.375
Come. We'll get the lawyer.

48:08.625 --> 48:10.417
- Shall we go?
- Come. We'll deal with this.

48:16.250 --> 48:17.667
Dad. I am ready.

48:17.958 --> 48:18.667
Ready for what?

48:19.208 --> 48:20.917
Please dad. Take
me along with you.

48:22.500 --> 48:24.792
Maaran. Dad is going
on an official trip.

48:24.875 --> 48:27.625
I will be away and so you have
to be the man incharge here.

48:27.750 --> 48:31.792
Mom asked me to go along with you.
The school is off tomorrow.

48:34.292 --> 48:35.917
Did your mom say that?

48:38.708 --> 48:40.042
Wait. I'll talk to her.

48:40.708 --> 48:43.292
Mom, Dad has agreed.
Pack my clothes as well.

48:47.542 --> 48:49.000
He has fooled me with
an empty suitcase.

48:49.875 --> 48:51.000
You little rogue!

48:53.792 --> 48:56.542
Pack both our clothes
in a single suitcase.

48:57.250 --> 48:58.417
I can't be carrying
extra baggage.

49:01.458 --> 49:03.125
- Hey Maaran.
- Dad.

49:03.125 --> 49:05.250
- It's getting late.
- I am ready.

49:05.333 --> 49:05.833
Hi darling!

49:08.958 --> 49:11.625
Didn't I ask you to pack
everything in a single suitcase.

49:12.375 --> 49:18.292
Maaran, the charger, towel and soap
is in this bag. Remind dad about it.

49:20.167 --> 49:21.000
Shall I leave?

49:21.292 --> 49:24.333
Be careful. Don't
go away from dad.

49:24.917 --> 49:25.833
Be safe.

49:26.042 --> 49:28.875
- Bye dear.
- Take care.

49:30.458 --> 49:32.917
- Amma, dad is leaving.
- Bye dad. Be safe.

49:34.042 --> 49:36.375
Ok darling. Take care of mom.

49:37.083 --> 49:38.667
- Bye
- Bye dad.

49:39.250 --> 49:40.000
Ok. I am leaving.

49:57.417 --> 49:58.542
- Uncle
- Sir

49:59.375 --> 50:01.667
- Sir. He is not anywhere here.
- Uncle.

50:04.375 --> 50:05.875
Where have you taken uncle?

50:07.917 --> 50:10.542
Hey! Who are you? Why are
you creating trouble here?

50:10.625 --> 50:11.375
Get out of the station now.

50:11.583 --> 50:14.292
- Where is my uncle?
- Uncle? I don't know any uncle.

50:14.500 --> 50:16.833
- Where have you taken him after the remand?
- We never remanded him!

50:16.958 --> 50:18.458
- We didn't remand anyone.
- They are playing a game.

50:18.583 --> 50:19.667
Don't bluff.

